My ad has been pending approval for 4 days now

Hi Jordan, I'm sorry to hear that your ad has been pending for so long. Could you let me know if this is a new account and if your business has been verified? This will help me provide more specific guidance.
I created this account 4 days ago

Thanks for the information, Jordan. Since your account is new, it might be pending verification. To proceed with the verification process and have your account approved, please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners.

Great, Jordan! Thank you for sending the email. Our team will review the information and update you on your account status as soon as possible. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
Do you have a conversion tracking setup tutorial for clickbank product sales?

Yes, we do have a tutorial for setting up conversion tracking for ClickBank product sales. You can follow the steps in this article to set up a ClickBank Postback on NewsBreak: [How to set up a ClickBank Postback on NewsBreak](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/23746617571341-How-to-set-up-a-ClickBank-Postback-on-NewsBreak). If you need any further assistance, feel free to ask!
